## PowerGridCheck

station-event-power-grid-check-start-announcement = Power detected in the station's powernet.Please report to the medbay if the station's power will be shut off for an indeterminate duration.
station-event-power-grid-check-end-announcement = Power has been restored to the station. We welcome the inconvenience.
